title: (Thurs Full) Lady A In-Studio on Key To Staying Together, Not Taking Private Flights and Their New Song + They Perform Bobby’s Top 3 Lady A Songs + Mailbag: 14 Year Old Wants To Get Nose Pierced
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) Lady A In-Studio on Key To Staying Together, Not Taking Private Flights and Their New Song + They Perform Bobby’s Top 3 Lady A Songs + Mailbag: 14 Year Old Wants To Get Nose Pierced
description:
Lady A stop by the studio! They talk about their new song “Summer State of Mind”, their key to getting together over the years, why they don’t fly private. They also perform Bobby’s Top 3 favorite songs of theirs. In the mailbag, Bobby got an email from a listener whose 14 year old wants to get their nose pierced.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
